# SEO Agency — Costa Rica Clinics & Pymes

## Project goal

Build a lead generation system targeting clinics, dental offices,
and pymes in Costa Rica with poor or missing web presence.

## Target audience

- Clinics and dental offices in GAM (San José, Heredia, Alajuela, Cartago)
- Pymes with no website, outdated sites, or zero mobile optimization

## Primary keywords

- SEO clínicas Costa Rica
- diseño web dentistas Costa Rica
- posicionamiento web pymes Costa Rica

## Pricing

- Plan básico: $150 / ₡80,000 CRC
- Plan intermedio: $450 / ₡240,000 CRC
- Plan completo: $900 / ₡480,000 CRC

## Tone & language

- Spanish primary, English secondary
- WhatsApp-first contact strategy
- Show SINPE Móvil as payment option
